Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经结束了 死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.91,0:00:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要结束的 是你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你 Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.27,0:01:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.88,0:01:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能动？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.40,0:01:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.83,0:01:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该已经穿透脊椎让她晕过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是Zero啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.13,0:01:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就再插狠点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.74,0:01:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你体内的中心所在之物…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.71,0:02:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没人联络我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条隧道 一直通到哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听绘理说 前面貌似有个很大的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在听她说详情之前 通信机就被打烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:05:02.00,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Flight 03 「Zero」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那…是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵蚀？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香奈 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你是什么人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都休想坏我们的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.83,0:05:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空手就弹开了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让船起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要留在这颗星球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复不了原状了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她再继续攻击的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Zero」？那是指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是所谓的真核物质
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的原生体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到竟然在这颗星球上存活至今
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是同伴了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知是否是那知性体的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero往显著扭曲的方向得到了进化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不再跟我们是同种了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是敌人咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果硬要分类的话 这话是没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 马上传达给她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓来的女孩都在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们俩都被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.21,0:08:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的是那些女孩子啊 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数据已经采集完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她专注于那边 就不会过来碍我们的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花怜学姐 理沙子老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抓走的女孩子都在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 不知道怎么打开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门就是不开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女孩不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.46,0:09:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 原来你被插了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.03,0:10:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空军战机 已经准备好起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞到目标上空要多久时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达目标的预定时刻为 1500
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计赶不上目标发射呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果它要飞去卫星轨道的话 肯定会往东边上升
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.95,0:10:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航空母舰什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经往目标的预测路径进发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(战鹰1号 准备滑行)\NEagle 1 Clear for Taxi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(23号跑道)\NRunway 23
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(收到 准备滑行)\NRoger Clear for Taxi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(23号跑道)\NRunway 23
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从时钟塔上方搬到这种地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 现在就将她们搬到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.07,0:11:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要怎么弄 都被那些类似触手的东西固定着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到关键时刻 只能「强行」将她们放下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华 这触手用枪能打断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.22,0:11:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可以啦 不过现在没枪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 这事可以包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.47,0:12:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绘理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 把这些女孩救出就算任务完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面还剩几个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让你继续往前走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狗不挡道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标正后方 Vampire 01正在上升
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 她是准备执行我们的破坏要求吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.14,0:17:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事不过三！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标的路径方角发生变化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上升速度正在下降
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vampire 01 久等了 骑兵队到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始对目标发起总攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足够击灭目标
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Vampire 01
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在要在你们这边着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.77,0:20:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.15,0:20:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绘理 花怜学姐 先把路空出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.84,0:20:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人家这么担心 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 算了 放过她了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样事件就解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抓走的学生 也送去医院了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情告一段落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:20:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 大小姐 哪里算解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.85,0:21:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一堆要怎么处理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 总会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还总会有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻女孩的肌肤就是漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.44,0:21:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我说的不是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.77,0:21:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏孩子接下来要受惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 事情就是这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「是这样」？是算哪样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说要惩罚她们嘛 惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吧 船长 你想怎么搞都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.27,0:22:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各攻击机队 作战完成
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标已经完全破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错 干得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.34,0:22:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Silver Eagle 我是Pink Sapphire
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.66,0:22:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Silver Eagle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.58,0:22:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执行B计划 目标已经抓到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.86,0:22:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.80,0:22:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mission Complete(任务完成)！


